                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8387" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1296</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2410 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“资”滞“业”瘀，对症下“药”——星网锐捷分拆锐捷网络上市</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Lack of funding, stagnation of development, and the right medicine for the right problem - Fujian Star-net spun-off Ruijie Networks Listed</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">张瑞琛，李彤，高灵煊，黄君</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">福建农林大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">福建星网锐捷通讯股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">通讯业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">19 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">分拆上市；星网锐捷；锐捷网络</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Spin-off Listing;Fujian Star-net Communication;Ruijie Networks</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">随着分拆新规定在2019年年末颁布，很多大型企业都开始着手准备，因为分拆上市不仅可以缓解企业融资压力，还可以使得母子公司更好的聚焦主营业务，提升母子公司之间的正向协同效应。本案例以2022年11月21日锐捷网络成功分拆上市为主要故事线，通过向学员介绍星网锐捷和锐捷网络的发展背景，探讨其分拆上市的动因及过程，并将分析视角聚焦于星网锐捷分拆锐捷网络上市的融资原因、方式及金额，简单描述其分拆上市的效果以及分拆上市给企业带来的影响。本案例旨在引导学员应用理论于实践的能力，提高学员独立思考与分析能力，帮助学生理解分拆上市存在的情况，启发学员对分拆上市现象的思考。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">With the new regulations on spin-offs issued at the end of 2019, many large companies have started preparations because going public through spin-offs can not only relieve the financing pressure on enterprises, but also enable parent and subsidiary companies to better focus on their core businesses and enhance positive synergy between them. This case study focuses on the successful spin-off and IPO of Ruijie Networks on November 21, 2022. By introducing the development background of Fujian Star-net and Ruijie Networks to students, it explores the motives and processes behind the spin-off and IPO. The analysis in this case study is centered on the financing reasons, methods, and amounts of Fujian Star-net spinning off Ruijie Networks for IPO. It briefly describes the effects of the spin-off and the impact it has on the company. The aim of this case study is to guide students in applying theory to practice, enhancing their ability to think independently and analyze critically, helping them understand the circumstances surrounding spin-offs and IPO, and inspiring students to reflect on the phenomenon of spin-offs and IPO.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《财务管理》、《公司理财》、《资本运营》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">业务集中理论；融资需求理论；管理层激励理论；归核化战略理论；融资战略理论；事件研究法</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-06</td>
                            </tr>
